snippet.title: Chainsaw Man – The Movie: Reze Arc Official Trailer (2025)
snippet.description:
For the first time, Chainsaw Man slashes his way onto the big screen in an epic, action-fueled adventure that continues the hugely popular anime series. Denji worked as a Devil Hunter for the yakuza, trying to pay off the debt he inherited from his parents, until the yakuza betrayed him and had him killed. 

As he was losing consciousness, Denji’s beloved chainsaw-powered devil-dog, Pochita, made a deal with Denji and saved his life. This fused the two together, creating the unstoppable Chainsaw Man. Now, in a brutal war between devils, hunters, and secret enemies, a mysterious girl named Reze has stepped into his world, and Denji faces his deadliest battle yet, fueled by love in a world where survival knows no rules.

Based on the original work “Chainsaw Man” by Tatsuki Fujimoto (Serialized in Shueisha’s “Shonen Jump+”). Sony Pictures will release Chainsaw Man – The Movie: Reze Arc in US theaters on October 29, 2025.

snippet.title: La Ambulancia - Jessi Uribe
snippet.description:
“LA AMBULANCIA” – Jessi Uribe
Disponible en todas las plataformas digitales 👉 [link de streaming]

En este nuevo sencillo, Jessi Uribe abre su corazón y nos lleva a una historia intensa de despecho, dolor y desahogo emocional.
Con una narrativa cargada de simbolismo, “La Ambulancia” refleja cómo las heridas del alma pueden ser más profundas que las físicas, representando ese amor que se va y deja cicatrices imposibles de ocultar.

🎥 El videoclip, grabado en Bucaramanga, muestra escenas cargadas de dramatismo: una ruptura que desencadena un llamado de emergencia, la llegada de una ambulancia y el reflejo del vacío que deja un corazón roto. Con una estética juvenil y cinematográfica, Jessi se proyecta como una estrella global dentro de la música popular y la cumbia. https://JessiUribeOficial.lnk.to/LaAmbulancia
